{[%evp 0,22,28,12,75,69,66,69,59,17,22,16,16,10,38,39,32,22,26,-6,27,8,29,-7,2] [#]} {Black to move} 9... h5 $1 (9... Bb4 {Now 10. g4 would've gave me a pleasant edge. ½-½ (29) Alonso Rosell,A (2493)-Narciso Dublan,M (2532) Sabadell 2011}) 10. g4 hxg4 11. hxg4 fxg4 12. Bxg6+ Ke7 $1 13. Qg2 Bh6 {[%cal Gf6f5] We threat f5} 14. Bd3 f5 $15 {[%cal Gd7f6,Gd8d6,Ye7d7,Yd7c7] Suddenly Nf6 and Qd6 and our position is insanely good.} *

